// Lots of help and resources from Steve (sgodbold)

Set up for Vim:

 -- Install Vundle --
	git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

 -- Install all plugins --
	:PluginInstall (inside of vim)


Set up for tmux:

Place the file tmux.conf in either ~/ for user settings, or /etc/ for global
settings

Add to your bash.rc: TERM=screen-256color [[ -z "$TMUX" ]]

Leader mapped to C-a
